jlg-form.description:
追加属性:

 model-value:object,json渲染form绑定的formData数据源

 form-json?:T_JlgForm_FormJsonItem[],json渲染表单各项

 grid-layout-props?:I_Grid_Layout_Props,布局组件props

 gather-props?:object,数据采集单独object

 重置属性:

 label-position?:E_JlgForm_LabelPosition,form-item标签布局位置

 [element-plus el-form,点击查看](https://element-plus.org/en-US/component/form.html#form)

jlg-form-item.description:
追加属性:

 validate-rules?:T_FormValidatorRulesOptionRecord,内置校验规则参数

 重置属性:

 prop?:string,仅支持string，多层级对象用a.b格式

 [element-plus el-form-item,点击查看](https://element-plus.org/en-US/component/form.html#formitem)
